To reveal the effect of different processing methods on charge recombination. The dependence of Voc and Jsc on light intensity (Plight) are measured. The slope of Voc versus Plight is adopted to examine the type of recombination [34], as shown in Fig. S2. The slopes for BC-type, LBL-type and SAA-LBL-type devices are 1.20, 1.13 and 1.12 kT e−1, respectively. By fitting the Jsc-Plight curves with Eq. S1, the α\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
